            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)截至台北時間11日03:56股價下跌11.39美元，報216.35美元，跌幅5%，成交量58,614,657（股），盤中最高價228.25美元、最低價216.33美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.9%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-2.71%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-3.54%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-6.2%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.4%</li> <li>近 1 月：-4.41%</li> <li>近 3 月：+2.34%</li> <li>近 6 月：+33.45%</li> <li>今年以來：+3.81%</li></ul></section></main>",
